data.description: Great 4 bedroom in the heart of Parchment! Located near schools, Kindleberger Park, the library, and all that Gull Road has to offer, this home offers 4 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. There are spacious rooms and hardwood floors throughout. There is also a new hot water heater. The main floor features a good sized living room with wood burning fireplace, formal dining room, and kitchen with appliances included in the sale. There is also a half bath on the main floor. The bedroom are all located upstairs along with the full bath. The basement is great for storage and has the laundry area. The backyard is fenced and there is a 2 car garage. This is a great home that is ready for new owners and includes a 1 year home warranty for peace of mind!
